dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 10 feet contour interval, and spot heights. Includes guide to numbered features, street index, overprint legend, diagram showing boundaies. Includes 100,000 sheet 5281-5381 showing "Evacuation route Kampala - Entebee.", Includes overprinted evacuation route Kampala-Entebbe. Assembly point is indicated. "Limited revisions. Map information as of 1987." "DMA STOCK NO. Y932XKAMPALA." Copyright 1994 by the United States Government. No copyright clained under title 17 U.S.C.
